flowchart TB
  I["Intent\n工具名+input"] --> L["Registry Lookup\n查工具定义"]
  L -->|找不到| U["Unknown Tool\n生成拒绝观察"]
  L -->|找到| D["Tool Definition\nschema/risk/policy"]
  D --> W{"Visible?\n本轮可见吗"}
  W -->|否| K["Invisible Tool\n拒绝或要求重试"]
  W -->|是| V["Input Validate\n进入校验"]

  D:::hot
  W:::hot

  classDef hot fill:#fff3b0,stroke:#111,stroke-width:2px,color:#111;
